 {
  "text": "Hello, I am a waiter. I work at a small restaurant. Every day, I give the menu to the people. They look at the menu, and then they order. Many people say: I would like a coffee, please. Some people are very hungry, so they order a big plate of food. At the end, they ask for the bill. The food here is delicious, and the people are always happy.",
