  "file": "a10_listening_waiter.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "Hi, my name is Anna. Today I am at a restaurant with my family. I am very hungry. The waiter gives us the menu. I would like a salad and some water, please. My brother would like a coffee and a dessert. The food is delicious. After we eat, my father asks for the bill. We are happy, and we say thank you to the waiter.",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "a10_listening_customer.mp3"
 },
 {
